ğŸ“Œ Charts & Visual Data

Use libraries like Chart.js, Recharts, ApexCharts, or D3.js for dynamic graphs.

<LineChart data={data} />


These integrate well with Tailwind-styled containers.â€

ğŸ“Œ Tables & Lists

For history and leaderboard tables:

